template: SELECT MIN(movie_keyword.movie_id) AS movie_keyword_movie_id, MIN(title.id) AS title_id FROM movie_link, movie_companies, movie_keyword, keyword, company_type, title WHERE movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND movie_keyword.movie_id = title.id AND movie_link.movie_id = title.id AND keyword.id = movie_keyword.keyword_id AND company_type.id = movie_companies.company_type_id AND movie_companies.note NOT LIKE %s AND company_type.kind = %s AND title.production_year < %s AND movie_companies.note LIKE %s AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000 AND keyword.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death');
